some mutt is casing residences

00:24.606 --> 00:26.070
by, uh, McKinley Park.

00:26.073 --> 00:28.336
Now, we got our numbers
on break-ins down

00:28.339 --> 00:31.204
last month, so special
attention there, all right?

00:31.205 --> 00:33.338
Uh... some complaints

00:33.339 --> 00:36.132
regarding RMPs double-parked
in front of Portillo's.

00:36.135 --> 00:39.207
If you're there on dinner break,
find someplace else to park.

00:39.210 --> 00:40.937
Well, what if it's not
on our dinner break?

00:40.938 --> 00:42.571
Moving on.

00:42.572 --> 00:45.971
Uh... All right, listen up.

00:45.972 --> 00:47.867
"Pursuant to a consent decree

00:47.870 --> 00:49.653
between the City and various plaintiffs

00:49.656 --> 00:52.101
suing for actions alleged
to have been taken by members

00:52.104 --> 00:53.820
of the Chicago Police Department,

00:53.823 --> 00:57.369
attorneys from firms so
designated by a magistrate

00:57.372 --> 01:01.703
will be granted access to
CPD operations in the field."

01:01.706 --> 01:03.692
And that means?

01:03.695 --> 01:06.138
We got company. There's
some lawyers here

01:06.139 --> 01:08.338
who'll be doing ride-alongs tonight.

01:08.339 --> 01:11.138
Uh... as the chief of
patrol has directed,

01:11.139 --> 01:13.171
the department will
be in full compliance

01:13.172 --> 01:15.668
with the terms of said consent decree.

01:15.671 --> 01:17.140
The following units

01:17.143 --> 01:19.942
will have one such attorney
riding along with them:

01:19.945 --> 01:22.962
uh... Sector Charlie.

01:22.965 --> 01:25.460
And Sector David.

01:26.585 --> 01:28.184
Come on, let's remember,

01:28.187 --> 01:31.038
we're on the same side
with this. All right?

01:31.039 --> 01:32.445
That's it.

01:32.448 --> 01:34.981
Be safe.

01:36.472 --> 01:37.914
Here we go.

01:37.917 --> 01:41.325
There's one for you and one for you.

01:41.328 --> 01:42.757
Liability waiver?

01:42.760 --> 01:44.770
It's for our lawyers.
I'm sure you understand.

01:44.773 --> 01:45.637
"The undersigned

01:45.640 --> 01:48.338
hereby agrees to assume the
risk of death, personal injury,

01:48.339 --> 01:49.914
and/or property damage."

01:49.917 --> 01:52.286
I wouldn't worry too much
about that with Charlie Sector.

01:52.289 --> 01:53.904
What about David Sector?

01:53.905 --> 01:56.372
Make sure you sign all the pages.

01:59.406 --> 02:01.168
- We can always change sectors.
- No.

02:01.171 --> 02:03.062
No, no, no. I'm up for it.

02:03.065 --> 02:04.731
- Maia Rindell. Let's go.
- Yes.

02:04.734 --> 02:06.904
- Put this on.
- Wh... is this a bulletproof vest?

02:06.905 --> 02:09.204
No, it's a stab-proof vest.

02:09.205 --> 02:12.605
Protects against knives
and, uh, thrown acid.

02:12.606 --> 02:15.439
- Oh. Fun times.
- Yeah.

02:17.150 --> 02:19.706
- Lucca Quinn? This way.
- Yeah.

02:19.709 --> 02:21.576
Okay.

02:32.570 --> 02:36.789
